        1. Navigate to http://a.testaddressbook.com/sign_in
        2. Enter the username and password  //input[@name='user[email]']  //input[@name='user[password]']
        3. Click on sign in button      //input[@name='commit']
        4. Click on Addresses       //a[@data-test='addresses']
        5. Click on new address button  //a[@data-test='create']
        6. Enter the first name "Fernando"   id  address_first_name
        7. Enter the last name "Torres"     id address_last_name
        8. Enter the address 1 "Anfield Rd"     id address_street_address
        9. Enter the address 2 "Anfield"    id address_secondary_address
        10. Enter the city "Liverpool"      id address_city
        11. Choose a RANDOM option from the state dropdown  id address_state
        12. Enter the Zipcode "L4 0TH"  id  address[zip_code]
        13. Click on United States      id address_country_us
        14. Enter the birthday "03/20/1984"   id  address_birthday
        15. Enter the age "36"          address_age
        16. Enter the WebSite "https://www.google.com/"     address_website
        17. Enter the phone "8625747878"        address_phone
        18. Click on Climbing and Dancing   address_interest_climb  address_interest_dance
        19. Enter the Note "Never Back Down"        address_note
        20. Click on Create Address button      //input[@value='Create Address']
        21. Verify if the first name is "Fernando"      //span[@data-test='first_name']
        22. Verify if the last name is "Torres"         //span[@data-test="last_name"]
        23. Click on Addresses                      //a[@data-test='addresses']
        24. Click on Edit button                    //a[text()='Edit']
        25. Change the first name as "Peter"        address_first_name
        26. Change the last name as "Crouch"        address_last_name
        27. Click on Update address             //input[@value='Update Address']
        28. Verify if the first name is "Peter"         //span[@data-test='first_name']
        29. Verify if the last name is "Crouch"             //span[@data-test="last_name"]
        30. Click on Addresses                      //a[@data-test='addresses']
        31. Click on Destroy                        //a[text()='Destroy']
        32. Confirm deleting the address            switch
        33. Verify if the address was removed       [data-test='notice'
        34. Quit the browser*/
